item.title: 2 killed in attack outside synagogue in Manchester, England; suspect dead
item.description: Authorities said a vehicle and stabbing incident outside a synagogue in the English city of Manchester was a terror attack.

item.title: How could a government shutdown affect travel around the U.S.?
item.description: A prolonged government shutdown, as occurred in 2018, could lead to long lines at TSA checkpoints and economic losses, experts warn.

item.title: What is a government shutdown? Here's what happens when funding runs out
